nanny (0.4.0) unreleased; urgency=medium

  * Added Twilio SMS notifier.
  * Read X-Forwarded-For Header before using req.RemoteAddr for name (ubergesundheit/read-forwarded-for-header).
  * Fixed correct timeout message (ubergesundheit/notify-correct-timeout).
  * Added Slack webhook (ubergesundheit/slack-notifier).
  
 -- Lukas Nemec <lu.nemec@gmail.com>  Mon, 13 Aug 2018 13:11:15 +0000

nanny (0.3) stable; urgency=medium

  * IP address is appended to signal name, so it doesn't need to be
    unique.
  * Added debian packaging.
  * Added the option to use human readable duration representation, e.g.
    "1m15s".

 -- Lukas Nemec <lu.nemec@gmail.com>  Fri, 29 Jun 2018 13:39:15 +0000

